{
  "texts": [
    "GPA-GCN is designed for two prediction tasks: predicting gene-related traits (Task-trait) and identifying potential trait-related genes (Task-gene).",
    "Effect of k-NN algorithm.",
    "Our proposed tool is developed based on the GCN framework by graph sampling with the feature and topology graph.",
    "The k-Nearest Neighbor (k-NN) algorithm is used to construct a full graph based on node features and network topology.",
    "For each target node, the k most similar nodes are selected as its neighbors in the graph."
  ]
}